# Collapsible Sections

::: details Advanced Server Configuration
### Configuration Parameters

**Required Environment Variables:**
```bash
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@localhost:5432/db
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379
JWT_SECRET=your-secret-key-here
API_PORT=3000
```

**Nginx Configuration:**
```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name example.com;

    location / {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:3000;
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
    }
}
```

This content will be hidden initially and can be expanded by clicking.
:::

::: details Common Troubleshooting
### Frequent Issues and Solutions

**Database Connection Error:**
1. Check that PostgreSQL is running
2. Confirm credentials in environment variables
3. Check firewall configuration

**API 500 Error:**
1. Check server logs: `tail -f /var/log/app.log`
2. Check available disk space
3. Restart services if necessary
:::

