# Advanced Diagrams with Mermaid

## System Flow Diagram

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[User] --> B{Authenticated?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Main Dashboard]
    B -->|No| D[Login Page]
    D --> E[Validate Credentials]
    E -->|Valid| C
    E -->|Invalid| F[Show Error]
    F --> D
    C --> G[Select Action]
    G --> H[Create Project]
    G --> I[View Reports]
    G --> J[Settings]
    H --> K[Project Form]
    K --> L[Save to DB]
    L --> C
```

## Sequence Diagram - API Authentication

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant F as Frontend
    participant A as Auth Service
    participant D as Database
    participant R as Resource Server

    U->>F: Login Request
    F->>A: POST /auth/login
    A->>D: Validate Credentials
    D-->>A: User Data
    A->>A: Generate JWT
    A-->>F: JWT Token
    F->>F: Store Token
    F-->>U: Login Success

    Note over U,R: Accessing Protected Resource

    U->>F: Request Data
    F->>R: GET /api/data (with JWT)
    R->>A: Validate Token
    A-->>R: Token Valid
    R->>D: Query Data
    D-->>R: Data Results
    R-->>F: Protected Data
    F-->>U: Display Data
```

