# Architecture Diagrams

## System Architecture

```mermaid
C4Context
    title Project Management System

    Person(user, "End User", "Manages projects and tasks")
    Person(admin, "Administrator", "Configures system and users")

    System(webapp, "Web Application", "React SPA for project management")
    System(api, "Backend API", "REST API in Node.js")
    System(db, "Database", "PostgreSQL for persistence")
    System(cache, "Cache", "Redis for optimization")

    System_Ext(email, "Email Service", "SendGrid for notifications")
    System_Ext(storage, "Storage", "AWS S3 for files")

    Rel(user, webapp, "Uses", "HTTPS")
    Rel(admin, webapp, "Administers", "HTTPS")
    Rel(webapp, api, "Consumes", "REST API")
    Rel(api, db, "Reads/Writes", "SQL")
    Rel(api, cache, "Cache", "Redis Protocol")
    Rel(api, email, "Sends notifications", "API")
    Rel(api, storage, "Stores files", "S3 API")
```

